      "options": {
        "content": "### \u2139\ufe0f About This Report\nOne row per member \u00d7 card. **Click any tile** to jump to the table. Sourced from `reporting.dim_card` joined to `reporting.dim_member`.\n\n| Column | Source | Meaning |\n|---|---|---|\n| Client Member ID | `dim_member.client_member_id` | Your internal member identifier |\n| FIS Person ID | `dim_member.fis_person_id` | Stamped by Stage 7 after reconciliation |\n| FIS CUID | `dim_member.fis_cuid` | FIS cardholder unique ID |\n| FIS Card ID | `dim_card.fis_card_id` | Stamped by Stage 7 after reconciliation |\n| Card Status | `dim_card.card_status` | 1=Active \u00b7 2=Suspended \u00b7 3=Closed |\n| Start Date | `dim_card.issued_at` | Date card record created in pipeline |\n| Activated Date | `dim_card.activated_at` | First card use (null = not yet activated) |",
        "mode": "markdown"
      },
      "pluginVersion": "10.4.3"
    },
